### NorthPay - Onboarding Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### Register Contractor
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "contractor_test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "contractor",
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "Contractor",
  "phone": "1133344455"
}

###

### Login Contractor
# Obtener JWT de un usuario contractor autenticado
# Este token representa la identidad del usuario que completará su propio onboarding
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "contractor_test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Complete Personal Info
# Completa el primer paso del onboarding usando el JWT del contractor
# El endpoint usa la identidad del token, no permite actuar sobre otro usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/personal-info
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TOKEN_CONTRACTOR_ACA
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "Contractor",
  "country": "Argentina",
  "city": "Tandil",
  "address": "Calle falsa 123",
  "document_type": "dni",
  "document_number": "12345678",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01"
}

###

### Retry Personal Info (Should Fail)
# Verifica idempotencia: un contractor no puede completar este paso dos veces
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/personal-info
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TOKEN_CONTRACTOR_ACA
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "Contractor",
  "country": "Argentina",
  "city": "Rauch",
  "address": "Calle falsa 123",
  "document_type": "dni",
  "document_number": "12345678",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01"
}

###

### Register Operator
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator_test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "operator",
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "Operator",
  "phone": "1191112233"
}

###

### Login Operator
# Obtener JWT de un usuario autenticado con rol distinto a contractor
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator_test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Complete Personal Info with Operator Token
# Verifica control de acceso: solo contractors pueden usar este endpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/personal-info
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TOKEN_OPERATOR_ACA
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "Operator",
  "country": "Argentina",
  "city": "Rauch",
  "address": "Calle falsa 123",
  "document_type": "dni",
  "document_number": "12345678",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01"
}